## API Base URL

`https://api-production-a0a2.up.railway.app`

### Key Endpoints Used by iOS App

| Method | Path | Purpose |
|--------|------|---------|
| POST | /auth/login | Login (returns access_token) |
| POST | /auth/business/register | Register business |
| GET | /auth/me | Current user |
| POST | /auth/change-password | Change password |
| GET | /clients | List clients (returns plain array) |
| POST | /clients | Create client |
| GET | /visits | List visits (VisitListResponse with items/total/page/page_size) |
| POST | /visits | Create visit (requires client_id) |
| POST | /uploads/audio | Upload audio (multipart: visit_id + file + auto_process) |
| POST | /live/transcribe | Live transcription chunk (multipart: file, query: diarize, language) |
| GET | /pipeline/visits/{id}/status | Pipeline status |
| GET | /documents | List documents (supports client_id filter) |
| GET | /documents/{id}/download | Download document (auth required) |
| GET | /contract-templates | List OCR templates |
| POST | /contract-templates/upload | Upload template for OCR scanning |
| GET | /calendar/status | Google Calendar connection status |
| POST | /calendar/connect | Exchange OAuth code for Google Calendar |
| GET | /calendar/mobile-callback | OAuth redirect endpoint for iOS |
| GET | /billing/subscription | Get subscription details |
| GET | /billing/usage | Get usage limits |

### Upload Flow (CRITICAL)
1. Create visit: `POST /visits` with `{"client_id": "..."}` → get visit.id
2. Upload audio: `POST /uploads/audio` with multipart `visit_id` + `file` + `auto_process=true`
3. Pipeline auto-runs: transcribe → diarize → align → bill → note → contract

