## Known Issues Fixed

- Upload endpoint was /visits/upload → fixed to /uploads/audio
- Multipart fields were client_id/audio → fixed to visit_id/file
- Clients endpoint returned plain array, not wrapped
- Visit model was missing caregiver_id, pipeline_state, timestamps
- Client.status was non-optional but API returns optional
- requestRecordPermission deprecated on iOS 17+
- onChange(of:) two-param version is iOS 17+ only
- hasSeenOnboarding flag was skipping landing page → removed
- ISO8601 date parsing needed both fractional and non-fractional support
- Pyannote removed — diarization now handled by Deepgram (diarize=true)
- Route ordering: static routes before {id} params
- Dynamic Tailwind classes don't work — use static classes
- Google OAuth "Custom scheme URIs not allowed for WEB client type" → solved with backend redirect
- Contracts "not authenticated" download → added bearer token to download requests

